subject: Basketball

organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Kia Vaughn had 12 points and 11 rebounds and No. 5 Rutgers survived a scare from host Saint Joseph’s to hold on for a 56-50 victory Wednesday night.
